Wat is er?

01:55:38.060 --> 01:55:41.660
Hoger. Hoger.

01:55:56.130 --> 01:55:58.912
Dat is beter.

01:55:59.020 --> 01:56:01.912
Warm. Het is warm.

01:56:02.020 --> 01:56:07.470
Leg dus nu je linkerhand op de top van je hoofd...

01:56:10.920 --> 01:56:15.490
