01:56:19.160 --> 01:56:22.490
Dat is beter.

01:56:34.970 --> 01:56:39.530
Breng nu opnieuw je rechterhand omhoog

01:56:40.000 --> 01:56:42.832
en leg je linkerhand op de lever.

01:56:42.940 --> 01:56:47.490
Leg je rechterhand op je hoofd.

01:56:49.010 --> 01:56:52.450
De lever.

